data.description: Experience the epitome of spacious living in this expansive family home, perfectly situated on two generously-sized lots. Boasting a total of five well-appointed bedrooms, 3 accompanied by its own ensuite, this residence ensures privacy and comfort for every member of the household.   The interior of the home is thoughtfully designed to cater to various needs, featuring two distinct living areas that can effortlessly serve as additional office spaces or recreational rooms. Whether you're seeking a quiet sanctuary for remote work or a versatile area for family gatherings, these flexible spaces offer endless possibilities.  The heart of the home lies in its extra-large kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's dream come true. With an abundance of storage solutions and expansive counter space.   While the home boasts an array of desirable features, it is worth noting that it requires a touch of tender loving care to restore its full potential.
